* Overlaying known maps on screen when detected.
* Unify brain and dungeon. The code is confusing.
* Extend item identification help.
* Track spellbook read count
* Track spell learned turn
* Monitor pray safety
* Input macros (elbereth)
* Smash all the grid bugzeseseses

